docs.abstract: A 2016 engine failure set airlines and regulators on a path to more stringent testing. But the process wasn’t completed before an apparently similar failure left a woman dead.
docs.snippet: A 2016 engine failure set airlines and regulators on a path to more stringent testing. But the process wasn’t completed before an apparently similar failure left a woman dead.
docs.lead_paragraph: The engine failure that knocked a hole in the side of a Southwest Airlines Boeing 737 and left a woman dead on Tuesday was an extraordinarily unusual event, seemingly the result of a rare engine defect that scattered debris and knocked out one of the plane’s windows at 32,000 feet.

headline.main: As Engine Failed, F.A.A. Was Considering Rules That Might Have Made a Difference
headline.print_headline: Similar Type of Failure Worried Regulators in ’16

docs.abstract: Whether they’re digital photos on your smartphone or old negatives in your attic, here’s how to get started tackling your photo clutter.

docs.lead_paragraph: “I’ve seen it all,” says the award-winning National Geographic photographer Ami Vitale, about backing up her photos. “I’ve had hard drives fail throughout my career. For example, back when I first started as a photographer, I had a very nice hard drive system in my home, and the whole thing failed.” In retrospect, Ms. Vitale says, she would have definitely set the system up differently.

headline.main: A Beginner’s Guide to Backing Up Photos

docs.abstract: President Trump has talked about a huge infrastructure investment, but can we even make the trains run on time? Our beleaguered columnist is skeptical.
docs.snippet: President Trump has talked about a huge infrastructure investment, but can we even make the trains run on time? Our beleaguered columnist is skeptical.
docs.lead_paragraph: The Sunday before last, as I emerged tired and dispirited from Penn Station after a two-plus hour trip from the Newark airport, I found myself pondering President Trump’s campaign pledge “to spur $1 trillion in infrastructure investment,” a theme he raised  in this year’s State of the Union address and is expected to address again next week.

headline.main: From (Crumbling) Airport to (Broken) Escalators: An Infrastructure Odyssey
headline.print_headline: Getting Here From There: An Odyssey
